- Replace nistp224 with curve25519 http://cr.yp.to/ecdh.html

- Use secure hash of secret (SHA-256 or SHA-512) as encryption key

- Reset CBC state before each packet

- Set the IV to the encrypted sequence number

- Add more counters to srlogd for error packets

- Gradually migrate to protocol v2
  - Make srlogd drop all packets not starting with 0xffffffff
  - Add code to srlogd to handle the new protocol ("SRL2")
  - Migrate all senders to use protocol v2

- Switch to curve25519 http://cr.yp.to/ecdh.html
